extends content-layout

//- Janurary: Sales Distance
append foreground
  +fg-item('January', 'The Average Sale:<br> Over 2,000 miles')
    p In January we sold works between New York and Oslo, London and Los Angeles, Singapore and Houston.
    blockquote “Thanks to Artsy, we sold 3 works prior to the opening. The client felt comfortable buying the work, site unseen, because of the quality of presentation on the Artsy site.”
      br
      | – Deborah Herringer Kiss, Gallery Owner
append background
  +bg-item
    img( src='images/content/map.png' )
    .half-viewport-height

//- Feburary: Eye Contact
append foreground
  +fg-item('February', 'Eye Contact')
    p In 2013, we added our 1,000th category to The Art Genome project – the classification system for art that powers Artsy. Our favorite in February was “Eye Contact.”
    p During the year our Art Genome team analyzed over 44,000 artworks and applied over 700,000 categories.
    a.faux-underline( href="http://artsy.net/gene/eye-contact", target='_blank' ) Explore Eye Contact
append background
  +bg-item
    ul.two-column-images.two-column-left
      li
        img( src='images/content/eye-contact-thomas.jpg' )
        p Mickalene Thomas
        em Qusuquzah, Une Trés Belle Négresse 1,&nbsp;
          span 2012
        p Lehmann Maupin
        p $18,500
      li
        img( src='images/content/eye-contact-abramovic.jpg' )
        p Marina Abramović
        em Golden Lips,&nbsp;
          span 2009
        p Sean Kelly Gallery
      li
        img( src='images/content/eye-contact-longo.jpg' )
        p Robert Longo
        em Untitled (Leo)
        p Christie's Post-War & Contemporary Art
        p $250,000 - 350,000
    ul.two-column-images.two-column-right
      li
        img( src='images/content/eye-contact-roversi.jpg' )
        p Paolo Roversi
        em Tanel Bedrossiantz (Jean Paul Gaultier’s “Barbès” women’s ready-to-wear fall-winter collection of 1984–85),&nbsp;
          span 1992
        p Brooklyn Museum
      li
        img( src='images/content/eye-contact-vermeer.jpg' )
        p Johannes Vermeer
        em Girl with the Red Hat,&nbsp;
