//- March: The Armory Show
append foreground
  +fg-item('March', 'The Armory Show')
    p Artsy’s partnership with The Armory Show included 97% of exhibitors participating and over 200,000 visitors viewing 10 million artworks.
    p In 2013 Artsy covered 17 art fairs from around the world, including Art Basel in Basel, Hong Kong, and Miami; Frieze London; ArtRio; and Contemporary Istanbul.
    a.faux-underline( href="http://artsy.net/thearmoryshow", target='_blank' ) Revisit the fairs from 2013 on Artsy
append background
  +bg-item
    figure
      img( src='images/content/fairs-armory.jpg' )
      figcaption The Armory Show at Pier 92 and Pier 94 in New York
    figure
      img( src='images/content/fairs-dm.jpg' )
      figcaption Design Miami — Formlessfinder's “Tent Pile”
    figure
      img( src='images/content/fairs-frieze.jpg' )
      figcaption Frieeze – Geometric Mirrors VI by Jeppe Hein in the Frieze Sculpture park

//- May: Ragnar Relay
append foreground
  +fg-item('May', 'Ragnar Relay')
    p In May we ran the Ragnar relay. 26 hours and 52 minutes of continuous running. 197 miles covered. Beaten by teams like “U.S. Department of Minimal Effort” and “Fanny Pack Gold” but we got an A for effort.
    a.faux-underline( href="https://artsy.net/about/jobs", target='_blank' ) Run the relay with us in 2014
append background
  +bg-item
    ul.two-column-images.two-column-left
      li
        img( src='images/content/ragnar-pose.jpg' )
      li
        img( src='images/content/ragnar-camp.jpg' )
