    img( src='images/content/ragnar-course.jpg' )

//- June: JR
append foreground
  +fg-item('June', 'JR turns Artsy inside out')
    p In June the Artsy NYC team headed uptown to have our portraits taken by the artist JR; and soon after, displayed with pride across our 25th floor headquarters.
    a.faux-underline( href="https://artsy.net/artist/jr", target='_blank' ) Follow JR on Artsy
append background
  +bg-item
    img( src='images/content/jr-wide.jpg' )
    img( src='images/content/jr-close.jpg' )
    img( src='images/content/jr-inside.jpg' )

//- July: Open Source
append foreground
  +fg-item('July', '30th Open-Source Project Released')
    p In July we released our 30th open-source project. We love open-source at Artsy. It lets us build better software, faster. We also like to give back to the community by contributing to existing open-source libraries, and by releasing our own code under open-source licences.
    a.faux-underline( href="http://artsy.github.io", target='_blank' ) Go to Arty's Engineering Blog
append background
  +bg-item
    #background-code
      .viewport-height
      pre
        include code.txt
      .viewport-height
      img#background-code-mask.viewport-height( src='images/logo-mask.svg')

//- August: Art & Science
append foreground
  +fg-item('August', 'Art & Science')
    p In August Artsy’s 7th artist/engineer, 
      a( href='https://artsy.net/artist/damon-zucconi' ) Damon,
      | joined the team. We are now 66 artists, engineers, art historians, designers, curators, writers, and mathematicians. 40 of us are women, 26 men. 6 of us have kids, and 5 of us are avid Magic the Gathering players.
    a.faux-underline( href="https://artsy.net/about/team", target='_blank' ) Find out more about the roles at Artsy
append background
  +bg-item
    figure
      img( src='images/content/damon.jpg' )
      figcaption.artist-info
        p Damon Zucconi
        p Tetradic Edit, 2013
        p JTT Gallery
    .half-viewport-height

//- September: Art in your pocket
append foreground
  +fg-item('September', 'Art in your pocket')
    p In September we shrunk Artsy. 120,000 people downloaded our iPhone app–named a “Best new app” by Apple. Art lovers have viewed and saved more than 4 million artworks since the launch.
    a.faux-underline( href="http://iphone.artsy.net/", target='_blank' ) Download the Artsy iPhone app
append background
  +bg-item
    img( src='images/content/iphone-screens.jpg' )

//- October: Art in Schools
append foreground
  +fg-item('October', 'Art in Schools')
    p In October Artsy become an official part of public education in New York as a partner for Digital Ready – a program designed to help NYC public high schools use technology to improve their students’ readiness for college and careers. More than 25,000 open-access images on Artsy are freely downloadable for educational use.
    a.faux-underline( href="#", target='_blank' ) Learn more about how Artsy is used the classroom
append background
  +bg-item
    figure
      img( src='images/content/doe-kids.jpg' )
      figcaption Three students at Brooklyn International High School, one of ten schools participating in New York Citi’s Digital Ready program.
    figure
      img( src='images/content/doe-meeting.jpg' )
      figcaption Mayor Bloomberg and Chancellor Walcott announce the expansion of New York City’s Digital Roadmap for New York schools.

//- November: Better tools for Benefit Auctions
append foreground
  +fg-item('November', 'Better tools for Benefit Auctions')
    p November we partnered with Independent Curators International (ICI) to support their annual benefit auction. This year bidding wasn’t limited to the 300 people at the gala event. Anyone from around the world could participate from computer, tablet or mobile phone. All lots sold, and we helped raise 50% more than ICI’s target to support their educational programming.
    p For more information about our auctions, get in touch with us at&nbsp;
      a.faux-underline( href="mailto:partners@artsy.net", target='_blank' ) partners@artsy.net
append background
  +bg-item
    img( src='images/content/auction-phone.jpg' )
    img( src='images/content/auction-ici.jpg' )
    img( src='images/content/auction-marina.jpg' )

//- December: Gallery meets Collector
append foreground
  +fg-item('December', 'Gallery meets Collector')
    p In the last week of December we introduced more collectors to galleries than in the entire year of 2012.
    a.faux-underline( href="http://artsy.net", target='_blank' ) Find your new favorite work on Artsy
append background
  +bg-item
    img( src='images/content/dec-graph.jpg' )